# Teen Facts Website

A responsive, interactive website that displays interesting statistical facts about humans. The website features a modern design with animated cards and a shuffle functionality.

## Features

- Responsive design that works on both mobile and desktop devices
- Interactive fact cards with hover animations
- Shuffle functionality to randomize fact order
- Modern gradient background
- Clean, accessible typography
- Mobile-first approach with responsive breakpoints

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (with Flexbox)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- No external dependencies required

## Getting Started

1. Clone this repository or download the HTML file
2. Open `index.html` in any modern web browser
3. Click the "Shuffle Facts" button to randomly reorder the facts

## Browser Support

The website works in all modern browsers including:
- Chrome (latest)
- Firefox (latest)
- Safari (latest)
- Edge (latest)

## Customization

To add or modify facts, edit the `facts` array in the JavaScript section of the HTML file. Each fact should follow this structure:

```javascript
{
    title: "Fact Title",
    content: "Fact content goes here"
}
